snippet.title: EpicBloodQuest gameplay
snippet.description:
EpicBloodQuest is a school project for PôleIID.
This game is a retro shooter for hardcore-gamer in pixel-art style, made with GameMaker Studio 2.
Sprite and animations were made with Aseprite.
